      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person to believe it. It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for someone to take this home and enjoy it as much as I have!",
