    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear, 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring surgical precision through the twisties. The chassis is structurally immaculate with a reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings, maintaining its original torsional rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black with a deep, swirl-free luster, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically untouched.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
