      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled, preserving the deep, mirror-like finish of the original paint with zero chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats are supple without a single crease, the 'new car' scent lingers, and every surface is free of wear. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and strictly OEM parts. Every button, electronic component, and seal functions perfectly. This is a turn-key example for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
