    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and runs like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for the open road, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
