    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanically superlative example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. The engine exhibits perfect compression and the double-VANOS timing system has been proactively overhauled to ensure optimal torque delivery across the entire rev range. The chassis is structurally immaculate; the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014addressing the platform's primary weak point\u2014and the suspension retains its razor-sharp factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Power is channeled through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a limited-slip M-differential with no lash or noise. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing no signs of oxidation, and the interior Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
